Digital Bandpass Modulation


Linear Modulation (bandwidth efficient)

   - ASK  ---->   OOK (Non-coherent)
          ---->   ASK-SSB ----> VSB (easy implementation)
          ---->   QAM 
          
   - PSK  ----> Differential PSK (Non-coherent)
          ----> OQPSK, p/4-QPSK (Low cost, power efficient)


Orthogonal Modulation (power efficient)

   - FSK  ----> Non-coherent FSK
          ----> Coherent FSK ----> Continuous-Phase FSK (narrow bandwidth) ----> MSK (Binary) ----> GMSK (narrow bandwidth)
   
   - Orthogonal Modulation ----> Bi-orthogonal modulation (bandwidth efficient)
                           ----> Trans-orthogonal modulation (power efficient)
